title: ETH v1 Update: Raise $DPI collateral cap
body:
Intro: This is a vote to raise the collateral cap of PERP on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market.
Proposal: Listing Committee
Rational: DPI is currently capped out on the ETH v1 market.

For:
Raise collateral cap of $DPI to 21,189 DPI or $7M USD.
Against:
Do not make any changes to the ETH v1 market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
